txt.en: Head out into the Ettenmoors and collect the materials needed to construct the gate that will seal the front of Lugazag tower.
'Do not test my patience. The Free People will return.'
Orders are to collect items from around the Ettenmoors so that a gate can be constructed to keep the Free People out of Lugazag. Best get to it.

'Do you think I am going to return to Gramsfoot without having done all I can to defend this tower? No! I need you to go get the material we need to seal up the front of this tower and keep those Free People from breaching!'
Deliver the materials to Dum√ªl at Lugazag
'Quick work and efficient too. I will make sure to report that to the War-tyrant. No, I don't need your name.'
Defence: Build a Gate at Lugazag
